        "testimonial_ViaQWP": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "stars_count": 4,
            "text": "<p><strong>Very pleased with the quality</strong></p><p>The cardigan is very well made, with neat stitching and a soft, warm feel. It sits nicely on the shoulders and keeps its shape throughout the day. The small details, like the buttons and finish, make it feel like a quality piece.</p>",
            "author": "Rebecca L."
          }
        },
        "testimonial_kkmtHU": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "stars_count": 4.5,
            "text": "<h3><strong>Excellent customer service</strong></h3><p>The customer service was friendly and helpful, and delivery was quicker than expected. The quality of the items exceeded my expectations. Highly recommend.</p>",
            "author": "Eva H."
          }
        },
        "testimonial_YbACKj": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "stars_count": 4.5,
            "text": "<h3><strong>Excellent value for the money</strong></h3><p>Been buying clothes for years — this one stands out. Thick, quality fabric, great fit, and very comfortable. Warm without feeling heavy. Excellent value for the price. Would order again.</p>",
            "author": "Amelia S."
          }
        },
        "testimonial_EVBL3U": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "stars_count": 5,
            "text": "<h3><strong>Lovely quality</strong></h3><p>Lovely piece. Feels well made, keeps its shape, and looks neat with everything I own. Comfortable, simple, and good quality for the price. Very pleased.</p>",
            "author": "Natalie P."
          }
        },
        "testimonial_EkikKj": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "stars_count": 5,
            "text": "<h3><strong>Great fit and comfort</strong></h3><p>Great fit and very comfortable. Soft but sturdy fabric, and it looks exactly like the photos. Flattering and easy to wear all day. Very happy with it.</p>",
            "author": "Sophie M."
          }
        },
        "testimonial_YYYGhJ": {
          "type": "testimonial",
