            "icon_width": 48,
            "subheading": "",
            "title": "FAREWELL...",
            "content": "<p>Hi, I’m Claire, founder of Miller Melbourne.</p><p>For nearly 10 years, this little boutique has been a big part of my life. What started as a small dream slowly grew into something really special.</p><p>But life changes. <strong>My daughter Sarah i</strong>s growing up quickly, and I’ve realised it’s time for me to spend more time with my family.</p><p>Because of that, I’ve decided to close this chapter. Before we do, we’re holding one final <strong>Clearance Sale — up to 60% off</strong> to clear the remaining pieces in our store.</p><p><strong>Thank you so much for all your support over the years. It truly means a lot.</strong></p><p>– Claire Miller</p>",
            "link_text": "",
            "link_url": "",
            "background": "#ffffff",
